毒品、麻醉藥品或其他相類之物，致不能安全駕駛。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e5%8e%9f%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c7%2c20220225%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,原交簡,7,20220225,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"原交簡","JNO":"7","JDATE":"20220225","JTITLE":"公共危險"}